OL,3,CChildren's plaques among dozens of
OL,4,Cgraves vandalised at Muslim graveyard
OL,6,FMore than 80 graves, including those
OL,7,Fof babies and children, have been
OL,8,Fvandalised at a Muslim burial site
OL,9,Fnear Watford.
OL,11,FPolice said plaques were damaged at
OL,12,FCarpenders Park Lawn Cemetery over the
OL,13,Fweekend in what appeared to be a
OL,14,Fdeliberate attack on a specific
OL,15,Fsection of the site.
OL,17,FA funeral service provider said it was
OL,18,Falerted by a bereaved family who had
OL,19,Fburied a loved one at the site.
