OL,3,CChildren's plaques among dozens of
OL,4,Cgraves vandalised at Muslim graveyard
OL,6,F"Lots of concerned families and lots
OL,7,Fof phone calls, lots of emails have
OL,8,Fpoured through," Wadi Funeral Care
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,F"It's had a huge impact. It's not long
OL,12,Fago that Woodcock Hill Cemetery, not
OL,13,Ffar away from here, was also
OL,14,Fdesecrated.
OL,16,F"People feel that these sorts of
OL,17,Fattacks are becoming more frequent. I
OL,18,Fcannot understand how anyone could
OL,19,Fdesecrate a grave, a graveyard
OL,20,Fsomewhere that's supposed to be for
OL,21,Fpeace and serenity.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/7
