OL,3,CChildren's plaques among dozens of
OL,4,Cgraves vandalised at Muslim graveyard
OL,6,F"We were first contacted by a lady
OL,7,Fwhose baby is actually buried here,
OL,8,Fand we helped her bury her baby here
OL,9,Fless than a year ago.
OL,11,F"So that's what prompted us to act and
OL,12,Ffrankly these families haven't had the
OL,13,Ftime to sit down and reflect on who,
OL,14,Fwhat, why. They're just shocked.
OL,16,F"And at the moment they just need the
OL,17,Fsupport from the council, from the
OL,18,Fpolice that they have been getting and
OL,19,Ffrom the community," Wadi Funeral Care
OL,20,Fadded.
