OL,3,CChildren's plaques among dozens of
OL,4,Cgraves vandalised at Muslim graveyard
OL,6,FIshrat Zuberi visited her father's
OL,7,Fgrave at the cemetery and couldn't
OL,8,Funderstand why anyone would do such a
OL,9,Fthing.
OL,11,FShe said: "I'd like to think that they
OL,12,Fweren't in their right mind. I can't
OL,13,Fcomprehend that anybody rational would
OL,14,Fdo something like this.
OL,16,F"I'm speechless. I haven't actually
OL,17,Fprocessed this because it's so awful.
OL,19,F"My father is a respected man in the
OL,20,Fcommunity and many other respected
OL,21,Fmembers of my family as well.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/7
