OL,3,CChildren's plaques among dozens of
OL,4,Cgraves vandalised at Muslim graveyard
OL,6,F"So it's awful, it's shocking."
OL,8,FThe cemetery is owned by Brent Council
OL,9,Fwhich is contacting all affected
OL,10,Ffamilies.
OL,12,F"Family liaison officers from the
OL,13,Fpolice will be available to support
OL,14,Fevery single person," said Councillor
OL,15,FMuhammed Butt the leader of Brent
OL,16,FCouncil.
OL,18,F"We're also collecting all the
OL,19,Fevidence and all the damaged name
OL,20,Fplates.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/7
