OL,3,CChildren's plaques among dozens of
OL,4,Cgraves vandalised at Muslim graveyard
OL,6,F"And we will make sure that we work
OL,7,Fthrough sensitively with the
OL,8,Findividuals who are impacted to see
OL,9,Fhow we can support them and replace
OL,10,Fthe name plates and everything else to
OL,11,Fput it back to what it is.
OL,13,F"And we're also taking advice from the
OL,14,Fpolice as to what other actions that
OL,15,Fmay be necessary.
OL,17,F"If it means having patrols in the
OL,18,Fnext few days and weeks coming
OL,19,Fforward, we will absolutely do that.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/7
