OL,6,F"And if it means working with the
OL,7,Fcommunity to understand what their
OL,8,Fissues and concerns are, because it
OL,9,Fwould be quite traumatic hearing that
OL,10,Fsomeone's loved one's grave has been
OL,11,Fdesecrated - and we need to make sure
OL,12,Fwe're supporting everyone down there
OL,13,Fas well," he added.
